name: COLLECT: Here=Now
description:
2/2 of the Here=Now cinemagraph series 

A commentary on the current state of collectors on Hic Et Nunc, where time and place are often irrelevant when it comes to collecting.   

A transformative take on a photo by Indro Muktiono. The original photo might be included as a part of a future photo collection. Digitally produced.

 2160 × 2704 seamlessly looping cinemagraph in MP4 format.
